--- Lokk / Axis ---

  Lokk smiles, making his imediate suspicion. "Well then, now I know your names... but, I don't know you. Where did you come from, and what faction are/were you with?" Lokk says near the ship for now. Although having new recruits for his faction was inticing, he would not miss screening the bots to make sure they were telling the truth.
  Axis stands tall beside Lokk, eyeing the bots impassivly. He couldn't see anything wrong with the bots, but that didn't mean that Lokk wouldn't find anything.
